{
  "stem": "942.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there were hundreds of baskets, you know, like baskets that high.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Like a bushel basket, sort of.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there were guys with shovels lined up and with the rest of us with baskets.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they filled up our baskets with this chemical.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And where it was rain or shine, you know, We have to carry-- oh gee, this rhymes, rain or shine, we had to carry this lime, you know-- this chemical.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was heavy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So from this pile where we picked it up, we put it on our shoulder, and we went to the field.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, you know, 150 of us, we lined up in sort of like [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] a staggered way.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then we took the basket off our shoulder and put it on our knees.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we scooped it up with our hand and just sprayed it on the field, you see.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And when the basket was gone, you went back for another load.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "At this went on, you know, day on and day on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And after about three, four days, this chemical, this lime, ate-- started to eat away the skin on our fingers.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I remember, I could see the bone sticking out on my fingers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And my kneecap was visible, because the skin was all-- it was actually rotting away.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And this stuff was leaking.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Because if it was raining, you know, this stuff was leaking and leaching out from the baskets.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And our outfits, our skins, we were all covered with this white lime.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And our skins were itching, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We couldn't wash this off.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And this was a terrible time, you know, to-- I'll never forget that we look like white ghosts, you know.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "You could never wash this off.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
